high_descs: Turn right for one step, turn left to face the desk.
Pick up the pencil sitting on the desk to the right of the chair.
Stand holding the pencil up.
Put the pencil on the second shelf horizontal to the dog and the tip facing the keys.
Turn around for one step, turn left and walk past the bean bag chair, take a left and then a right, and walk toward the dresser at the foot of the bed.
Pick up the pencil on the right.
Turn right for one step, turn right again and walk past the bean bag chair then turn right to face the desk.
Put the pencil on the second shelf, vertically behind middle of the existing pencil with the tip up and pencil leaning back on the dog statue.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on the hutch shelf, one horizontal and one vertical.

high_descs: Take a step to the right to face the right end of the desk.
Pick up the pencil on the desk.
Look up to face the shelf with a statue on it.
Place the pencil on the shelf with the statue.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the dresser.
Pick up the pencil to the right on the dresser.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn right to face the desk.
Place the pencil on the shelf of the desk with the other pencil.
anns.task_desc: To move two pencils to the shelf of the desk with the statue.

high_descs: Turn right and face the desk on your left.
Take the pencil from the desk in front of you.
Look up at the shelves in front of you.
Place the pencil on the top shelf in front of you.
Turn right and face the dresser in front of you.
Take the blue pencil off the dresser in front of you.
Turn around and face the desk on your right.
Place the pencil on the top shelf of the desk in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Move pencil to the top self of the desk.
